          <span>Experimental Physics</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="inline-block w-3 h-3 rounded-full" style="background:#10b981"></span>
          <span>Astrophysics</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="inline-block w-6 border-t-2 border-gray-400"></span>
          <span class="text-gray-400">Shared concepts (thicker = more)</span>
